          <h2 id="conduct">Code of Conduct</h2>
          <p>Customers must submit accurate, respectful, and lawful content. Bodyshops must provide honest, professional quotes and services. We reserve the right to suspend access for violations.</p>

          <h2 id="feedback">Feedback Policy</h2>
